episodes.title: Leader of cultlike 'Zizian' group pleads not guilty to federal gun charge
episodes.description:
Ziz LaSota, referred to in charging documents by what her lawyer called her deadname, Jack LaSota, was charged with one count of possession of firearms and ammunition by a fugitive from justice.

episodes.title: Leader of cult-like group linked to multiple killings arrested in Maryland
episodes.description:
The leader of the so-called "Zizians" - a cultlike group which is connected to a series of violent incidents across the country - has been arrested in Allegany County, Maryland.
